  m_text: "Use arrow keys to move.\n\nPress Z to attack, C to use special move, and
    A to use skill.\n\nWhen swapping is ready, press spacebar to swap between two
    character types: Melee and Ranged, each with different attack method and skillsets.
    HP and aggros of the current character will be carried through.\n\nYou can also
    delay swapping to build up charges (up to 2). \nA charge will be consumed the
    next time you swap to reduce the swap cool-down time to 0."
